  "text": "Furthermore, we have agreement (within grid resolution) with the data given in [CITATION_1] . Also compiled in Table 1 is the data from the limiter experiments conducted in [CITATION_2] (although not explicitly discussed in the language of limiters by the authors of that work). In [CITATION_3] the authors give vortex centre data for the positivity rule ( Fig. 1) and for ELBM (which we interpret as containing a hidden limiter). In [CITATION_4] the positivity rule is called FIX-UP.",
